{"tid":2432231,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"關禮傑 跳樓情節 (真人版)","createTime":"2021-03-04T07:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T16:32:01.000Z","uid":127905,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0fc33996b293a565733ccf7312f9fd2688e1ef","tid":2432231,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/d8/Bigjump.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20140322143329\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd8%2FBigjump.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F400%3Fcb%3D20140322143329&h=c09f38b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210304/photo/bkn-20210304015552369-0304_00822_001_01p.jpg?20210304130725\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210304%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210304015552369-0304_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20210304130725&h=9333ea21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅磡華豐街7至8號衡豐樓，昨晚(3日)11時許，警方接報上址8樓有天台屋起火，濃煙沖天，且傳出爆炸聲響，多名街坊報警求助。消防到場開動2條喉及調派2隊煙帽隊灌救，約30分鐘後將火救熄，逾20名住客自行疏散到安全位置，火警中無人受傷。<br />\n現場消息指，有人目睹火警發生時，其中一間天台屋冒出濃煙，<span class=\"red\"><strong>屋內有一名印度漢爬出窗外坐於晾衫架上逃生，惟濃煙不斷由窗外噴出，他為保命冒險跳過3米外的毗鄰6號的大廈逃生，他並無受傷</strong></span>，在場協助警員調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210304/bkn-20210304015552369-0304_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210304%2Fbkn-20210304015552369-0304_00822_001.html&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyvxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=fc36c017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210304/bkn-20210304015552369-0304_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n勁過晒所有連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70848adf99fc45106111da9ee4e9ae706ba09ab","tid":2432231,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"3米我諗唔會勁得過連登仔...<br />\n紀律部隊<span class=\"green\">立定</span>跳遠都要兩米幾先滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d3d4886f7f660ba35ca9e3bad5bc6b3c211c0d","tid":2432231,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f70848adf99fc45106111da9ee4e9ae706ba09ab","tid":2432231,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"3米我諗唔會勁得過連登仔...<br />\n紀律部隊<span class=\"green\">立定</span>跳遠都要兩米幾先滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05be305502bfe1f2514fe5a1fe5ea4923f3ec1a","tid":2432231,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14d3d4886f7f660ba35ca9e3bad5bc6b3c211c0d","tid":2432231,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f70848adf99fc45106111da9ee4e9ae706ba09ab","tid":2432231,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"3米我諗唔會勁得過連登仔...<br />\n紀律部隊<span class=\"green\">立定</span>跳遠都要兩米幾先滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:44:51.000Z","msg":"有助跑、可以用手落地<br />\n如果咁都reach唔到3米，應該可以準備身後事"},{"pid":"22f7b15e0477f9f909ddf6fc3c46d3f21232a8fb","tid":2432231,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/14/220723_5ae7913f6807df46b75b3623120c3b3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F14%2F220723_5ae7913f6807df46b75b3623120c3b3a.png&h=9fee8047&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7092e1e7536b9814f6baa77b9d1ced4e2d9033b","tid":2432231